media-online-drive - Media Drive Online/Offline

USAGE:
    media-online-drive

DESCRIPTION:
    Temporarily online a USB media drive for resilvering, then
    offline it. Handles GELI encryption and ZFS pool operations.

PROCESS:
    1. Attach encrypted USB device
    2. Online device in ZFS pool
    3. Wait for resilvering to complete
    4. Offline device and export pool
    5. Detach encrypted device

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-media-management-usb-device DEVICE
        USB device path

    -conf-media-management-encryption-key-file FILE
        GELI encryption key file

    -conf-media-management-pool POOL
        ZFS pool name

    -conf-media-management-resilver-wait SECONDS
        Wait time between resilver status checks

EXAMPLES:
    media-online-drive
